#12201
roaming maurader~
A roaming maurader~
A roaming marauder of the wastelands stands here, eyeing you with greed.
~
A sneer is worn upon this dirty man's face like an old friend.  His clothes
are raggish and in shambles, while his hair is cut in a punk mohawk style.
His arms and legs are skinny and withered from lack of proper food and
water.  He roams this desert with only a goal taking from others to benefit
himself.
~
