kenshiro ken fist north star~
Ken~
The Fist of the North Star marches here, destroying buildings in his passing.
~
After his 'death', Ken, Fist of the North Star, awakens from the ground
to see his rebirth.  Seven scars anoint his chest, given to him by his
former friend, Shin.  His anger and vengeance emanate from him like a
sickly black smoke.  His eyes glow from beneath a long black cloak, showing
only pure unadulterated anger.
~
