#12275
In Ryuuken's Dojo.~
This place is utterly amazing.  There are two statues of battling
gods against the north wall.  The room is almost utterly dark except
for a slight glow coming from small oil lamps in the corner of each room.
You can smell meditation inscence in the air thickly and a greasey stench
of sweat.  This room is safe from any form or battle or torment.
~
